      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Containers: \n- PR: major.minor.patch-stage.<hash>\n- REL: major.minor.patch\n- latest\n- floating: semver\n\nDevcontainer Features:\n- semver\n- latest\n\nPython\n- PR: <major>.<minor>.<patch><stage><sequence>\n- REL: <major>.<minor>.<patch>\n\nGo (v-semver)\n- PR: v<major>.<minor>.<patch>-<stage>.<sequence>\n- REL: v<major>.<minor>.<patch>\n\nTerraform (v-semver)\n\nGitHub Actions/RWF: semver",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Containers: \n- PR: major.minor.patch-stage.<hash>\n- REL: major.minor.patch\n- latest\n- floating: semver\n\nDevcontainer Features:\n- semver\n- latest\n\nPython\n- PR: <major>.<minor>.<patch><stage><sequence>\n- REL: <major>.<minor>.<patch>\n\nGo (v-semver)\n- PR: v<major>.<minor>.<patch>-<stage>.<sequence>\n- REL: v<major>.<minor>.<patch>\n\nTerraform (v-semver)\n\nGitHub Actions/RWF: semver",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
