      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "support:\n- prefix\n  - v\n- major\n- minor\n- patch\n- stage\n  - dev, a, b, rc\n- sequence\n  - inputs: commit sha, file contents hash, build number\n  - interpreted: ghcr, pypi, gh releases, git tag",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "support:\n- prefix\n  - v\n- major\n- minor\n- patch\n- stage\n  - dev, a, b, rc\n- sequence\n  - inputs: commit sha, file contents hash, build number\n  - interpreted: ghcr, pypi, gh releases, git tag",
